msgstr "**Social**: Specifies social media-related content within the email."

#: ../../advanced_email_management/toc.rst:239
msgid "**Header Named**: Specifies a custom email header name."
msgstr "**Header Named**: Specifies a custom email header name."

#: ../../advanced_email_management/toc.rst:241
