#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:128
msgid "Using Folders"
msgstr "Using Folders"

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:130
msgid ""
"Folders serve to arrange both incoming and outgoing email correspondence."
" You have the option to create your folders or utilize predefined system "
"folders:"
msgstr ""
"Folders serve to arrange both incoming and outgoing email correspondence."
" You have the option to create your folders or utilize predefined system "
"folders:"

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:132
msgid ""
"**System folders** - These folders are immutable; they cannot be "
"relocated, renamed, or erased. The system includes the following folders:"
msgstr ""
"**System folders** - These folders are immutable; they cannot be "
"relocated, renamed, or erased. The system includes the following folders:"

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:134
msgid "**Inbox**: The primary destination for new incoming email messages."
msgstr "**Inbox**: The primary destination for new incoming email messages."

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:135
msgid "**Sent**: Contains a copy of all outgoing emails."
msgstr "**Sent**: Contains a copy of all outgoing emails."

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:136
msgid "**Drafts**: Emails you have composed but not yet sent."
msgstr "**Bozze**: e-mail che hai composto ma non hai ancora inviato."

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:137
msgid ""
"**Junk**: Incoming emails suspected to be spam or junk, although not "
"definitively, are directed here. You can sift through these messages, "
"moving or deleting them as necessary. If left untouched, they are "
"automatically purged according to the administrator's settings."
msgstr ""
"**Junk**: Incoming emails suspected to be spam or junk, although not "
"definitively, are directed here. You can sift through these messages, "
"moving or deleting them as necessary. If left untouched, they are "
"automatically purged according to the administrator's settings."

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:138
msgid ""
"**Trash**: Deleted items are relocated here and remain until you manually"
" empty the trash or until automated purging occurs."
msgstr ""
"**Trash**: Deleted items are relocated here and remain until you manually"
" empty the trash or until automated purging occurs."

#: ../../basic_email_management/toc.rst:140
msgid ""
"**User-defined folders**: These folders, which you create to structure "
"your email, appear in the Folder list within the Overview pane. It is "
"important to note that top-level folder names must be unique and cannot "
"match any other top-level folder within your inbox."
msgstr ""
"**User-defined folders**: These folders, which you create to structure "
"your email, appear in the Folder list within the Overview pane. It is "
"important to note that top-level folder names must be unique and cannot "
"match any other top-level folder within your inbox."

